<DocsLayout title="LangGraph for Explicit State" section="Recipes"><Hero eyebrow="Recipe 01" title="LangGraph for explicit state" lede="Use LangGraph when the process needs visible state, conditional routing, persistence, interruption, and recovery." reading="12 min" difficulty="Implementation" prerequisite="Explicit State" />
<Question>Does the task need to pause and resume without reconstructing its progress from messages?</Question>
