<Decision question="When should LangGraph not be used?" answer="Do not use it for a single model call, a fixed linear workflow, or a process already well served by an existing workflow engine." alternative="No parallel framework for the same orchestration problem." />
<Takeaway>Use LangGraph to make state visible—not to make a simple task look agentic.</Takeaway></DocsLayout>